{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, evaluating the proposed framework or general LLM tools for long-term tasks requires a thorough assessment beyond task completion efficiency and user progress.",
    "It must encompass AI acceptance, ethical considerations, and privacy implications.",
    "Establishing an evaluation framework that addresses these dimensions is crucial for ensuring that LLMs' support for long-term tasks adheres to ethical standards and safeguards user privacy.",
    "Such a framework and general LLM tools are supposed to nurture a trust-based and ethically responsible human-AI collaboration society.Figure 1:1Figure 1: The GOLF framework: (a) a simplified illustration of a golf course (the background is generated by StableDiffusion); (b) a variation of the task taxonomy [25]; (c) the task process in the GOLF framework.",
    "The blue lines represent the potential path to complete the task, activity, or goal."
  ]
}